安装 niri：
pacman -S niri fuzzel thunar xwayland-satellite egl-wayland
安装登陆器：
sudo pacman -S greetd greetd-agreety
sudo systemctl enable greetd
配置：
/etc/greetd/config.toml
添加：
[
terminal
]
vt = 1

[default_session
]
command = "agreety --cmd niri"
user = "mcx"
即可生效：
sudo systemctl restart greetd
扫描检查：
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
reboot


